      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone looking for value. While it is mechanically functional and gets you from A to B, it does show some visible age, including some minor exterior scratches and noticeable wear on the interior upholstery. It has been used regularly, and while it doesn't have major mechanical failures, it may require some routine maintenance or minor cosmetic touch-ups in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for a buyer who prioritizes utility over perfection.",
