    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, clean, and it still runs like a dream. It\u2019s been a dependable companion for me, and I\u2019m sure it\u2019ll be just as great for its next owner. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis has been enhanced with essential subframe reinforcement and the VANOS system has been overhauled for peak variable valve timing performance. It retains sharp handling dynamics thanks to its M-tuned multi-link rear suspension and a responsive limited-slip differential. Though it shows minor aesthetic wear, the mechanical core is robust, offering a pure, analog driving experience with a linear power band and exceptional steering feedback.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "2019 SUV. Good condition. Single owner. Clean title. Minor exterior scratches. Mechanically sound. Recent oil change.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that perfectly balances performance and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, showing only minor road wear such as small stone chips on the front fascia and a light surface scratch near the trunk\u2014imperfections that do not detract from its overall impressive curb appeal. Inside, the cabin remains clean and inviting; the seats are free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and all power features, including the climate control and infotainment system, operate exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, backed by a documented history of regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance. The suspension is tight, providing a comfortable and quiet ride, while the tires show significant tread life. This car has been a reliable companion and is ready for its next owner to drive it home with confidence.",
      "price": 34800.0,
