    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven mechanical integrity. This specimen has been meticulously maintained, offering a refined driving experience that balances consistent performance with long-term reliability. With a sophisticated aesthetic and a robust service history, it represents an exemplary acquisition for the discerning driver who prioritizes quality and professional upkeep. Experience the assurance of a vehicle that meets our exacting standards for excellence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
