    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready for a new home where it can hit the road again! If you're looking for something reliable that still looks great and drives smoothly, this is definitely the one for you. I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have\u2014I'd love to see this car go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 29500.0,
